I am happt to announce that i was giving the opportunity to educate some young kids (college bound) the importance of having life insurance. Years ago we, myself didnt think it was something to worry about, i personally thought it was just for senior/retirement people to worry about but as time went by and i had my first child 23 years ago and experienced some losses, young and old i knew it was something i needed to look into for the security of my family and of course to have a piece of mind. Death had no time limit and if you look into our population today the young are going before the old. When i see these Go Fund Me pages it saddens me to see the situation these families are in. Im proud to say today that the people i educated on the importance of having Life Insurance took out policies and hopefully they will also spread the word and help prepare other people with a piece of mind. üòâüòä
